results.name: Index of the first occurrence of n in A066888.
comment: For all 0 < n < 1000, a(n) < A104272(n). - John W. Nicholson, May 22 2011
link: T. D. Noe, Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..10000
mathematica: nn=100; k=0; t=Table[0,{nn}]; cnt=0; While[cnt<nn, k++; prms=PrimePi[k(k+1)/2] - PrimePi[k(k-1)/2]; If[0<prms<=nn && t[[prms]]==0, t[[prms]]=k; cnt++]]; Join[{1},t] (* _T. D. Noe_, May 19 2011 *)
